CURRENT PRODUCTS
1. Reelin - Modified open-source design, ~70% PLA+
2. Rattlin - Modified open-source design, ~99% PLA+

Original design files: 
Reelin- https://www.printables.com/model/409481-cat-fishing-rod-toy-unglued-remix
Rattlin- https://www.printables.com/model/276723-flexible-snake-with-hole-for-string-cat-toy

Modifications: 
Reelin- Added logo, changed the size and scale of the line guides, created lures, used a lobster claw instead of a crabiner
Rattlin- Added a hole in the head of the snake

R&D HISTORY - Robotics Projects (2024)
Collaborative development with Kailash (@hifinoise):

Project 1: Battery-Operated Chase Ball (Rollin')
- Multiple iterations and trials
- Did not achieve desired functionality
- Discontinued

Project 2: Micromouse Adaptation (Rover)
- Based on Kailash's existing micromouse work
- Early-stage development
- Discontinued before completion

10% equity offered to Kailash for R&D work, declined

